reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits smartphone and easy to clean
reviews.reviewText: This bag is super easy to attach to your cup/bottle. Just make sure to tighten it enough that it won't slide down with weight. The charms it comes with are interchangeable with any croc type shoe charm. The material also makes it super easy to clean in a sink. I go to the beach and can just rinse the sand right off of it and it's instantly dry with one wipe. And it does fit my standard sized iphone with a case and a popsocket on it with no problems.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This water bottle pouch for Stanley products has been a great addition to our outdoor adventures. It's specifically designed to fit our Quencher Adventure 40oz and Stanley IceFlow 20oz/30oz bottles, providing convenient storage and protection. The set includes 10 charms and a silicone insulated cup, adding a touch of personalization and keeping our beverages at the right temperature. It's a practical and stylish choice for our outings.
